<div class="Post" id="post-31">
	<h3>Welcome to the Radiation Safety Institute of Canada. Our mission is prevention of cancer, occupational illness and injury from unacceptable exposure to radiation.  Our work is guided by the principle of “Good Science in Plain Language”®.</h3>
<h3></h3>
	<div class="clear"></div>	
</div>

