<div id="shaded"><p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-4839" alt="Tech" src="/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/Tech.png" width="167" height="122" data-mce-src="/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/Tech.png"></p><h2>Technical Services</h2><p>First-class radiation exposure monitoring and testing services are offered by our National Laboratories in Saskatchewan.</p><ul><li><a title="Radiation Exposure Services" href="/workplace/radiation-exposure-services" data-mce-href="/workplace/radiation-exposure-services">Radiation Exposure Monitoring for Miners (PAD)&nbsp;</a></li><li><a title="Home Radon Testing" href="/community/home-radon-testing" data-mce-href="/community/home-radon-testing">Radon Testing&nbsp;</a></li><li><a title="Leak Testing of Sealed Sources" href="/workplace/laboratory-services/leak-testing-of-sealed-sources" data-mce-href="/workplace/laboratory-services/leak-testing-of-sealed-sources">Leak Testing&nbsp;</a></li><li><a title="Radiation Instrument Calibration" href="/workplace/laboratory-services/survey-meter-calibration" data-mce-href="/workplace/laboratory-services/radiation-instrument-calibration">Radiation Instrument Calibration</a></li></ul></div>
<div id="noshade"><p><a href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services" data-mce-href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-4842" alt="Consult" src="/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/Consult.png" width="167" height="122" data-mce-src="/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/Consult.png"></a></p><h2><a href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services" data-mce-href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services">Consulting Services</a></h2><p>Experienced scientist are here to help you address an array of radiation related challenges, from licensing to workplace dispute resolutions.</p><ul><li><a title="CNSC Licence Application and Renewal Support Service" href="http://www.radiationsafety.ca/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/consulting/radiation-protection-program-documentation-services/cnsc-licence-application-and-renewal-support-service" data-mce-href="http://www.radiationsafety.ca/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/consulting/radiation-protection-program-documentation-services/cnsc-licence-application-and-renewal-support-service">CNSC Licensing Support</a></li><li><a title="EMF Surveys" href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/surveys/emf-surveys" data-mce-href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/surveys/emf-surveys">EMF Surveys&nbsp;</a></li><li><a title="X-ray Equipment Inspections" href="http://www.radiationsafety.ca/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/x-ray-equipment-inspections" data-mce-href="http://www.radiationsafety.ca/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/x-ray-equipment-inspections">X-Ray Equipment Inspections&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/consulting/studies-evaluations-and-reviews" data-mce-href="/workplace/surveys-and-consulting-services/consulting/studies-evaluations-and-reviews">Workplace Reviews</a></li></ul></div>
